#

Lemon Herb Grilled Chicken with Garlic Mashed Potatoes

45 min
$12.99
650 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freehigh-protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main CourseSide Dish

Tags:

grilledeasycomfort food

Description

Juicy grilled chicken marinated in zesty lemon and fresh herbs, paired with creamy garlic mashed potatoes.

Ingredients

  • chicken breasts: 4 pieces
  • lemon juice: 1/4 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic: 3 cloves
  • fresh herbs (parsley, thyme): 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • potatoes: 2 pounds
  • butter: 4 tablespoons
  • milk: 1/2 cup
